title: About OnRecord Title | Utah's Trusted Title & Escrow Partner
description: Meet the team behind OnRecord Title. 25+ years of title and escrow experience serving Utah real estate professionals with fast closings and personal service.
breadcrumb:
  - { name: "About", url: "/about/" }
---

<section class="hero hero-inner">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <p class="section-label" style="color: var(--color-accent);">About Us</p>
            <h1>A Modern Spin on Title</h1>
            <p class="subheadline">OnRecord Title was built for real estate professionals who are tired of slow, unresponsive title companies. We combine decades of experience with a commitment to speed and personal service.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="inner-grid">
            <div>
                <h2>Why We Started OnRecord</h2>
                <p>After 25+ years in the title industry, we saw the same problems over and over: blown deadlines, unreturned calls, and deals falling apart because the title company couldn't keep up.</p>
                <p>We started OnRecord Title to be the company we always wished existed — fast, transparent, and genuinely invested in your success. We're small on purpose. That means when you call, you get Keli or Ciara — not a call center.</p>

                <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Speed:</strong> 2-day title commitments, not 5-7</li>
                    <li><strong>Access:</strong> Direct line to your escrow officer, every time</li>
                    <li><strong>Flexibility:</strong> Mobile closings anywhere in Utah</li>
                    <li><strong>Pricing:</strong> Volume rates for professionals who send consistent business</li>
                    <li><strong>Experience:</strong> 36+ combined years of title and escrow expertise</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
                <p>Every file gets the same attention whether it's a $150K condo or a $5M commercial deal. We don't cut corners, we don't miss deadlines, and we don't disappear when things get complicated.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="inner-sidebar">
                <div class="sidebar-card">
                    <h3>Quick Facts</h3>
                    <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0;">
                        <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.85rem;"><strong>Founded:</strong> Midvale, Utah</li>
                        <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.85rem;"><strong>License:</strong> UT Agency #976568</li>
                        <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.85rem;"><strong>Experience:</strong> 36+ combined years</li>
                        <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light); font-size: 0.85rem;"><strong>Specialty:</strong> Residential & Commercial</li>
                        <li style="padding: 0.5rem 0; font-size: 0.85rem;"><strong>Service Area:</strong> Statewide Utah</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%; justify-content:center; margin-top:1.5rem;">Contact Us</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <p class="section-label">Our Team</p>
            <h2>The People Behind Your Closing</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="team-grid">
            {% for member in site.team %}
            <div class="team-card">
                {% if member.photo %}
                <img src="{{ member.photo }}" alt="{{ member.name }}" class="team-photo">
                {% else %}
                <div class="team-placeholder">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                <h3>{{ member.name }}</h3>
                <p class="team-title">{{ member.title }}</p>
                <p>{{ member.bio }}</p>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
